# Change Log
## -- Latest version --
### v1.3 - [2016-09-09] 
* Add function keys **F1** - **F4**
* **F1** - About LR2 Rival Ranking    
* **F2** - Modify Ir/ data in LR2     
* **F3** - View database status       
* **F4** - Reset log                  


